com.valentine.esp.demo

Class DemoData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.valentine.esp.demo.DemoData

  • public class DemoData
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the class that handles all the demo packets sent to it from the ESP Client. It stores the response packets and then puts them on the input queue as it receives request packets for the particular type of packet. InfDisplayData and AlertData Packets are put right on the queue with out storage. This effectively simulates a Valentine One with Checksum being plugged into the ESP buss.
